01:08:56,600 --> 01:09:08,000
<i> So, I could protect you even in the darkness </i>

997
01:09:08,000 --> 01:09:16,970
<i> You're my first ever lover </i>

998
01:09:16,970 --> 01:09:18,630
<i>At this moment,</i>

999
01:09:18,630 --> 01:09:21,710
<i>we should proudly enjoy what makes us happy.</i>

1000
01:09:21,710 --> 01:09:24,780
<i>It's so annoying when people
fall in love late in life.</i>

1001
01:09:24,780 --> 01:09:26,360
<i>A-Are they matching pajamas?</i>

1002
01:09:26,360 --> 01:09:28,350
<i>You look happy.</i>

1003
01:09:31,230 --> 01:09:33,500
<i>Does she know we're going on a trip?</i>

